        <h2 id="ai-features" class="mt-12 text-2xl font-bold text-navy-900">6. AI features disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-navy-900/85 leading-relaxed">
          The Service includes AI-assisted features such as quote suggestions, document
          classification, chargeable-event detection, and a retrieval-augmented chat assistant.
          <strong>AI outputs are suggestions, not authoritative determinations.</strong> They may
          be incomplete, inaccurate, biased, or out of date. You are solely responsible for
          reviewing, validating, and deciding whether to act on any AI output, including any quote,
